  <source>Groupe Hospitalier Pitie-Salpetriere</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine wether multimodal MRI (conventinal T1 and T2 sequences, diffusion, magnetization
      transfer, spectroscopy) is reproducible; to follow up a cohort of patients with early
      remmittent MS after treatment with interferon.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
